            "title": "盤中速報 - 星座能源(CEG-US)大跌5.44%，報322.65美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>星座能源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CEG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CEG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CEG-US</a>)截至台北時間16日22:30股價下跌18.55美元，報322.65美元，跌幅5.44%，成交量192,573（股），盤中最高價322.65美元、最低價322.65美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.13%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.27%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.25%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.76%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>星座能源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CEG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CEG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CEG-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.43%</li> <li>近 1 月：-7.49%</li> <li>近 3 月：-18.21%</li> <li>近 6 月：+3.9%</li> <li>今年以來：-9.79%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6313531",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 22:45:05",
            "source": "cnyes",
